{"tid":1168260,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"王嘉爾講韓文遭歧視！　親自唸出惡評…大器態度被讚爆","createTime":"2019-05-23T14:21:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-24T12:17:20.000Z","uid":74065,"like":15,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"9c6947a277d28bd8841d4275b7d293d3e546f915","tid":1168260,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T14:21:52.000Z","msg":"南韓7人男子團體GOT7近日帶著新歌《ECLIPSE》重歸樂壇，他們23日登上音樂節目《M! COUNTDOWN》演出回歸舞台，幾位成員趁著開啟直播與歌迷互動，怎料，留言卻出現種族歧視的英文字句，令歌迷憤恨不已，但王嘉爾（Jackson）忍住情緒，高EQ回覆留言，面對惡評的態度受到稱讚「回答得很大器」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4115/d4115142.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4115%2Fd4115142.jpg&h=04703084&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼王嘉爾講韓文遭歧視有口音，親自唸出惡評。（圖／翻攝自秒拍、王嘉爾IG、GOT7 IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4115/d4115143.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4115%2Fd4115143.jpg&h=c8da301a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n王嘉爾23日與成員開啟直播，並用韓文與成員間對話，認真看過每條留言的他，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">突然發現有酸民以帶有種族歧視的口吻回覆：「真有趣，Jackson講韓文，但聽起來還是很像Ching Chong（帶有種族歧視口音的意思）。」暗指他的口音依舊有中國腔調。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對此，王嘉爾並未選擇忽視留言，立刻將這段文字唸出來，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">親自回答：「你知道嗎，不要有負面的回覆，好嗎？讓我們保持積極的態度，讓我們的愛多於恨。」</span></span></strong>這段影片被粉絲PO出，令歌迷心疼他獨自在外打拼還得受到不平等對待，但也有人讚嘆他的應對得體。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db0ac9e3c24a4f09ad5ce7eb2b1318e33525fd46","tid":1168260,"uid":240447,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T14:22:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" cl